quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  33,63,"Anthuamakufunsanizaola. Nenakuti,“Mulunguyekha ndiye amene amadziwa za ilo. Kodi chidzakudziwitsani ndi chiyani za olali? Mwinatu lili pafupi!”"
  33,64,Ndithudi Mulungu watemberera anthu osakhulupirira ndipo wawakonzera moto woyaka
  33,65,Adzakhalamo mpaka kalekale ndipo iwo sadzapeza mtetezi kapena wowathandiza
  33,66,"Pa tsiku limene nkhope zawo zidzalangizidwe moto, iwo adzati, “Kukadakhala bwino kuti tikadamvera Mulungu ndi kumvera Mtumwi”"
  33,67,"Ndipo iwo adzati, “Oh Ambuye wathu! Ndithudi ife tidamvera atsogoleri athu ndi akuluakulu athu kotero iwo adatisocheretsa.”"
  33,68,“oh Ambuye wathu! Apatseni iwo chilango chowirikiza ndipo atemberereni iwo ndi matemberero ochuluka.”
  33,69,oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Musakhale ngati anthu amene adayankhula zinthu zoipa zokhudza Mose. Koma Mulungu adatsutsa zonse zimene anali kunena za Mose. Ndipo iye anali wolemekezeka kwa Mulungu
  33,70,oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Opani Mulungu ndipo muzinena mawu abwino
  33,71,"Iye adzasunga ntchito zanu pamalo abwino ndi kukukhululukirani machimo anu. Ndipo aliyense amene amamvera Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake, ndithudi, iyeyo wapeza chinthu chopambana"
  33,72,"Ndithudi Ife tidapereka udindo ndi chikhulupiriro kumwamba, pa dziko ndi pa mapiri koma zonse zidakana kulandira ndipo adauopa. Koma munthu adauvomera. Ndithudi iye ndi wosalungama ndiponso mbuli"
  33,73,"Motero Mulungu adzalanga amuna ndi akazi a chinyengo. Ndiponso amuna ndi akazi opembedza mafano. Ndipo Mulungu adzakhululukira anthu onse okhululupirira, amuna ndi akazi. Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndiponso mwini chisoni chosatha"